    <h1 class="mb-4">Best Way to Appear on Perplexity 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on testing across UK business websites</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Perplexity is the AI search engine that shows its working. Every answer comes with numbered source citations that link directly to the original page. For businesses, this means Perplexity is the AI platform most likely to send you actual traffic. It is also one of the fastest-growing, with over 15 million monthly queries.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Getting cited by Perplexity requires a different approach to ChatGPT or Gemini. Perplexity crawls the web in real-time for many queries, which means fresh, well-structured content has an outsized impact.</p>

